，流露於演出中，不刻意討好也少嘩眾取寵，分數高低、共鳴與否都無所謂；經由她的創作，素人力量爆發蔓延，外表平凡卻是一位非常有勇氣的小護士，徐佳瑩只想讓全世界聽得到她的創作。',1,0,1,64,11,0,'http://static.musixmatch.com/images/albums/5/5/2/6/6/4/11466255.jpg','http://static.musixmatch.com/images/albums/5/5/2/6/6/4/11466255_350_350.jpg','http://static.musixmatch.com/images/albums/5/5/2/6/6/4/11466255_500_500.jpg','','http://www.books.com.tw/exep/assp.php/justgps/exep/cdfile.php?item=0020132720&utm_source=justgps&utm_medium=ap-books&utm_content=recommend&utm_campaign=ap-201408',0,0),(414,'13881522','03bc56b2-1216-4a36-a5fb-f0ed6294fae7',158,'Lamusique','2010-11-05',0,'','','',0,'',1,0,0,10,11,0,'http://static.musixmatch.com/images/albums/nocover.png','','','',NULL,0,0),(412,'10859090','7bdf80e7-8914-4273-82e2-967e61edbab3',157,'離別之前: before leaving','1997-01-01',0,'','','',0,'',0,0,0,14,12,0,'http://static.musixmatch.com/images/albums/nocover.png','','','',NULL,0,0),(411,'10859430','2637b425-a803-4ebf-8822-950c39f6a7cd',157,'1997 采妮','1997-01-01',0,'','','',0,'',1,0,0,27,10,0,'http://static.musixmatch.com/images/albums/nocover.png','','','',NULL,0,0),(407,'10776283','8f7ed883-9bf3-4c93-87ea-3610747ffddd',125,'柯有倫','2005-08-19',0,'','','',0,'',1,0,0,51,12,0,'http://static.musixmatch.com/images/albums/9/4/1/7/8/7/11787149.jpg','http://static.musixmatch.com/images/albums/9/4/1/7/8/7/11787149_350_350.jpg','http://static.musixmatch.com/images/albums/9/4/1/7/8/7/11787149_500_500.jpg','http://static.musixmatch.com/images/albums/9/4/1/7/8/7/11787149_800_800.jpg',NULL,0,0),(394,'13880049','5667c586-b1a7-400f-b7d4-8acb4a1fd5f4',37,'I Will Miss You','2010-03-01',0,'','','',0,'',1,0,0,34,10,0,'http://static.musixmatch.com/images/albums/nocover.png','','','',NULL,0,0),(419,'13881496','139627de-02cd-4a04-bc59-03fef72ced98',158,'Everlasting Greatest Hits','2005-07-18',0,'','','',0,'',0,0,0,0,9,0,'http://static.musixmatch.com/images/albums/nocover.png','','','',NULL,0,0),(421,'13881474','2f0dc176-b690-43fc-9696-0c4f504aa3cb',158,'All the Best','2005-07-03',0,'','','',0,'